headline: FirstEnergy Foundation Donates $25,000 to American Red Cross
summary: The FirstEnergy Foundation has donated $25,000 to the American Red Cross to support its efforts to offer disaster assistance to families living in communities served by FirstEnergy Corp. (NYSE: FE) electric company Jersey Central Power & Light (JCP&L).

headline: Sempra Energy's Q1 Earnings Beat Estimates, Revenues Increase Y/Y
summary: SRE's Q1 earnings beat the Zacks Consensus Estimate by 19%. The top line increases 4.5% from the year-ago level.
